snippet.title: Singham Again |Jai Bajrangbali|Ajay,Akshay,Ranveer,Kareena,Deepika,Tiger,Thaman,Swanand,Rohit Shetty
snippet.description:
Experience the power of "Jai Bajrangbali" from Singham Again, starring Ranveer Singh. Sung by Srikrishna, Kareemullah, Arun Koundinya, and various artists, this electrifying anthem is composed by Thaman S with impactful lyrics by Swanand Kirkire. This Diwali, let the spirit of Lord Hanuman ignite the unstoppable energy of this action-packed track!

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Jio Studios Presents
In Association With Rohit Shetty Picturez & Devgn Films
In Association With Reliance Entertainment & Cinergy
 
Produced By
Ajay Devgn, Jyoti Deshpande & Rohit Shetty

Directed By Rohit Shetty

Star Cast:
Ajay Devgn, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Ranveer Singh, Akshay Kumar, Deepika Padukone, Tiger Shroff, Arjun Kapoor, Jackie Shroff

Credits : 
Programmed & Arranged by - Thaman S 
Lyrics - Swanand Kirkire
Acoustic Drums & Electric Rhythm: Thaman S
Drums & Band: The Gongura Band & Thamania 
Live Percussions: Anandan Sivamani
Drum & Beat EDM Works - Beyond Sound (T)
Additional Programming - Shashank Alamuru, Hari S R, Osho V
Cellos Viola Violins - Sandilya ( HYD ) 
Electric Bond Guitars - Subhani & Subashree 

Singers -
Srikrishna
Kareemullah
Arun Koundinya
Chaitu Satsangi
Sri Sai Charan
Sudhanshu
Ritesh G Rao
Saatvik G Rao
Prudhvi Chandra
Lakshmi Naidu
Adviteeya
Sruthi Ranjani
Pranati
Aishwarya Daruri
Sahithi Chaganti
Maneesha Pandranki
Shruthika
Lakshmi Meghana
Nadapriya
Vagdevi

Recorded at Prasad Studios (HYD) by Hari S R & 
V studios ( CHN) by Osho V
Vocal Supervision - Srikrishna

Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge ( Mumbai ) & 
New Edge ( CaL) 
New Edge Team -  Anup Gandharla & Prasad Maha

Musicians Co Ordinator - Manikandan 
Studio Manager - Seenu,Sridhar
Studio Assistance - Kannan,Lingam,Raju, Pawan & Ranjith

Lyrics:
Jai Hanuman gyan gun sagar
Jai Kapis tihun lok ujagar
Ram doot atulit bal dhama
Anjaani-putra Pavan sut nama
Mahabir Bikram Bajrangi
Kumati nivar sumati Ke sangi
Kanchan varan viraj subesa
Kanan Kundal Kunchit Kesha
Jai hanuman
Bajrang bali
Jai hanuman
Bajrang bali
 
 Antara 1
 
veer bajrangi Hanumaan
shreshth bhakton mein inkaa naam
aaye aaye kar lo pranaam
inki dhadkan mein ek hi  naam
 
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam raam bhadra Raam raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam jai shri Sita Raam
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam raam bhadra Raam raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam jai shri Sita Raam

raakshas  dhwansaka
Dharma sanrakshakah
Raam naam poojakah
sankat mochakah
 
paap vinaashakah
Yogi yog  sadhakah
shatru gan paatakh
vajra roop ghaatakh
  
anjani putra hanumaan
vaayu ke sut hanumaan
inki bhakti mein chaar dhaam
inke mukh mein bas raam naam
 
bhakta hai ,
virakta hai ,
vajra hai
sashkta hai
hriday cheerey hrdya mein hai raaam
 
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Jai Shri Ram
 
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Sita Raam
 
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Jai Shri Ram
 
Raam raam bhadra Raam Sita Raam
Raam Raam Raam Bhadra Raam Sita Raam

snippet.title: Family Diaries | Web Series | Ep1 - The Old Scooter | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
Family Dairies follows the everyday life of a middle-class family‚Äîa father, mother, and their only son‚Äîas they navigate the ups and downs of modern family life. The father works hard to provide, while the mother nurtures the family‚Äôs emotional core. Their son faces the pressures of growing up, balancing family expectations with his own dreams. Each episode highlights the family's interactions with friends and relatives, portraying the challenges, joys, and lessons that come with maintaining love and harmony in their lives.

A Dreamz Unlimited Production.

How to make Chakali Bhajani Recipe at home | how to make chakali bhajani¬†
 ‚Ä¢ Wash the rice, moong dal, urad dal, chana daal, separately
 ‚Ä¢ Keep them on to separate strainers for 10 mins to remove excess water
 ‚Ä¢ Then spread them onto separate cotton cloths under shadow for 2-3 hrs
 ‚Ä¢ Then heat up a heavy bottom kadhai, add rice & rosat it until rice changes the color to more whitish, get fluffy, once done take them onto a dry cotton cloth
 ‚Ä¢ Then into the same kadhai roast chana daal on low flame until they get light grill marks, once done, pour the roasted chana daal onto the roasted rice
 ‚Ä¢ Then dry roast moong dal followed by the urad daal & take them onto the cotton cloth
 ‚Ä¢ Then dry roast sabudana & poha separately on low flame & take them out
 ‚Ä¢ Lastly dry roast cumin seed & coriander seeds & take them out onto the roasted grains
 ‚Ä¢ Allow the roasted ingredients to cool down completely & them take them to a flour mill & grind fine powder
 ‚Ä¢ Our chakali bhajani is ready to make crispy chakali

How to make Kurkurit chakali recipe | how to make bhajanichi chakali recipe |
 ‚Ä¢ Take the bhajani flour into a large plate or parat.
 ‚Ä¢ to this add salt, sesame, carom seeds, chilly pw & mix everything well
 ‚Ä¢ Into a tadaka pan heat up oil, pour this piping hot onto the chakali bhajani flour, mix well & rub the oil all over the flour
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up some water, once water is about to boil turn off the flame, & knead the dough using hot water
 ‚Ä¢ carefully mix the flour using a spatula¬† into the hot water, cover it for 10 mins¬†
 ‚Ä¢ then using lukewarm water knead a tight dough
 ‚Ä¢ Our chakali dough is ready to make chakali.
 ‚Ä¢ take some dough from the ready dough, using some water knead the dough to make it soft (as shown in the video)
 ‚Ä¢ make a log out of it, put the log into the chakali mould, make the chakalis
 ‚Ä¢ heat up oil for frying the chakali, once oil is med hot, drop 3-4 chaklis, fry them on med flame
 ‚Ä¢ while frying keep the flame med, not too low or high

How to make Chakali Bhajani Recipe at home | how to make chakali bhajani¬†
 ‚Ä¢ Wash the rice, moong dal, urad dal, chana daal, separately
 ‚Ä¢ Keep them on to separate strainers for 10 mins to remove excess water
 ‚Ä¢ Then spread them onto separate cotton cloths under shadow for 2-3 hrs
 ‚Ä¢ Then heat up a heavy bottom kadhai, add rice & rosat it until rice changes the color to more whitish, get fluffy, once done take them onto a dry cotton cloth
 ‚Ä¢ Then into the same kadhai roast chana daal on low flame until they get light grill marks, once done, pour the roasted chana daal onto the roasted rice
 ‚Ä¢ Then dry roast moong dal followed by the urad daal & take them onto the cotton cloth
 ‚Ä¢ Then dry roast sabudana & poha separately on low flame & take them out
 ‚Ä¢ Lastly dry roast cumin seed & coriander seeds & take them out onto the roasted grains
 ‚Ä¢ Allow the roasted ingredients to cool down completely & them take them to a flour mill & grind fine powder
 ‚Ä¢ Our chakali bhajani is ready to make crispy chakali

How to make Kurkurit chakali recipe | how to make bhajanichi chakali recipe |
 ‚Ä¢ Take the bhajani flour into a large plate or parat.
 ‚Ä¢ to this add salt, sesame, carom seeds, chilly pw & mix everything well
 ‚Ä¢ Into a tadaka pan heat up oil, pour this piping hot onto the chakali bhajani flour, mix well & rub the oil all over the flour
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up some water, once water is about to boil turn off the flame, & knead the dough using hot water
 ‚Ä¢ carefully mix the flour using a spatula¬† into the hot water, cover it for 10 mins¬†
 ‚Ä¢ then using lukewarm water knead a tight dough
 ‚Ä¢ Our chakali dough is ready to make chakali.
 ‚Ä¢ take some dough from the ready dough, using some water knead the dough to make it soft (as shown in the video)
 ‚Ä¢ make a log out of it, put the log into the chakali mould, make the chakalis
 ‚Ä¢ heat up oil for frying the chakali, once oil is med hot, drop 3-4 chaklis, fry them on med flame
 ‚Ä¢ while frying keep the flame med, not too low or high

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Last Episode 90 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 17th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: Koolyug - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Welcome to Koolyug ‚Äì jahan hoti hai virtual duniya aur asli emotions ki takraar! Amit, jo asli rishton ki ehmiyat samajhta hai, aur uski girlfriend Tanya, jise sirf fame aur followers ki fikr hai; ye dono khade hain ek ajeeb mod par. Likes aur comments ki race mein kya unka pyaar bacha rahega? Ya phir ek unexpected twist inki duniya ko hamesha ke liye badal dega? snippet.title: NOOL PAROTTA | Thread Parotta Recipe Cooking In Village | Lachha Paratha | Soft Layered Parotta
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a special thread parotta recipe. This parotta has different names in different places. In Karachi, it is called "Lachha Paratha." In our place, we call it "Nool Parotta." This Parotta has different layers: on the top, it's crunchy, and in the middle, it's very soft.

Parotta lovers can try it at home. The taste is very delicious!

#samvishal #niyathi #Kadhal Serkaadho #mediamasons 
"Kadhal Serkaadho," composed by SamVishal, is a heartfelt melody that beautifully captures the essence of love. The soothing vocals and gentle instrumentation create an immersive experience, inviting listeners to lose themselves in its emotional depth. With poignant lyrics, it resonates with anyone who has ever experienced the complexities of romance.

snippet.title: Sundeep Sharma Stand-up Comedy -College Fest
snippet.description:
I perform at College festivals quite regularly and connect with the young and brilliant minds that will shape up the future of our beloved nation; India/Bharat. As a rule, I reach colleges/universities much before my performance time and like to learn and research about what is going on in those bright and Khurafati minds. I also do it for the selfish reason that it takes me back to my own college days when I was one of the most khurafati young men but also, one of the top debaters in the country. I eat at the college canteens and like to attend their after parties if I am invited, P.S: I am always invited :D This bit is part fact, part fiction, but it definitely covers some hilarious incidents that happened along the journey of me doing college festival shows across the country, if you like this one and share it extesively and comment on this one, I shall make this a series and will come up with more in this series, for that, you will have to call me to your college festival this season. I am shameless and selfish, I want great food, great ambience and great agricultural environment around me :D Enjoy Karo Doston !!

Credits: 
Venue courtesy: The Habitat-Comedy and Music Cafe
Shot by: Dishang Popat, Vivian Castelino Harsh Shah and Karan Kundnani
Live sound recording: Yash Rajiv Barse, Siegen Moopnar
Editor: Ankit

Kaffara 2nd Last Episode 89 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 16th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.title: Chhaila | Shreya Ghoshal x Sunidhi Chauhan | Salim Sulaiman | Shraddha Pandit | Bhoomi 2024
snippet.description:

Jabse Woh Mila Hai

Mera Haal Kya Hai 
Uski Nazar Ne

Chhaila Woh Mera Chhaila
Rom Rom Mein Hai Phaila
Kaise Kar Gaya Mujhko Paagal

Ishq Jaise Mera Pehla, Pehla

Sargam

Chhaila Mera Chhaila, Always & Forever

Sargam

Chhaila Mera Chhaila, Oo..

Antra
Hum Jab Mile The Uss Ne Kaha Tha Mujhse
Tere Bina Reh Na Paayenge

Sargam

Din Raat Baatein Karta Hai Mujhse Woh Toh
Kehta Hai Chal Bhaag Jaayenge 

Aashiq Woh Mera, Dhoondle Tu Tera
Sach Hai Kya Ab Tu Yeh Jaan Le

Chhaila Woh Mera Chhaila..

Kyun Insta Pe Stalk Mujhe Karta
Emoji Se Mere DM Ko Bharta 

Kabhi Dinner Pe, Movie Pe
Arre Kyun Date Pe Le Jaane Ko Woh Marrta

Har Waqt Mujhe Call Kyun Lagaaye (Kyun?)
Mujhe Drive Pe Bulaaye, Sataye Kyun? Kyun Mere Peeche Mandaraaye
Are You Serious?
Isi Liye Toh 

Yeh Khushfehmiyan Sahi Nahin
Woh Toh Mera Hai Tera Nahin 
Lagta Hai Tumko Maalum Hi Nahin Hai

Chhaila Mera Chhaila x2
Kaise Kar Gaya (Kar Gaya) Paagal

Chhaila Mera Chhaila
Rom Rom Me Hai Phaila
Kaise Kar Gaya Hai Mujhko Paagal

Sargam

Chhaila, He Ain‚Äôt No Lover
Paagal Kar Gaya, Kar Gaya
Kya Woh Mera
Chhaila, Mera Chhaila

Na Vo Mera Lover
Na Hai Vo Chhaila Mera

snippet.title: Brownie recipe in Tamil | Chewy Fudgy Brownie Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make brownie recipe in tamil. There are two types of brownies, cakey brownie which is dry and flaky and fudgy brownie which is softer and more chewy. Both brownies are different in their ratios of flour to fat content. For this recipe, we can use either chocolate bars or chocolate morsels. Also, in this recipe we have used egg but we can make an eggless version by substituting eggs with curd/yogurt.
#brownie #brownierecipeintamil #brownierecipe 

Friends, please do try this brownie recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
150g semi sweet chocolate or dark chocolate
50g Nuts or chocolate
1/2 cup Butter (100g)
3 Eggs
1.5 cup Sugar (300g)
1/4 cup Oil
1 tsp Vanilla extract
1 cup Maida (125 g)
1/2 cup cocoa powder (40g)
1/8 tsp Salt
8 inch square baking pan 175c/350f for 28 min

Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Do you remember what it felt like? The first time you stepped onto campus? Butterflies in your  stomach as you eagerly awaited the world before you. From the joy of personalizing your own nook in the dorm to chatting away with newly made friends in the canteen, these memories will forever remain. 
 
#ReMann will take you on a nostalgic journey through time, while also gently holding the hands of those who are setting out on it for the very first time.
